# Probe set: thinking campaign (Campaign 14 thinking block)
# Format: {"id", "campaign", "category", "lang", "prompt", "expected_cluster"}
# Run with: python3 meta/scripts/brain_map.py probe --checkpoint $CKPT --probes training/corpus_admin/probe_sets/thinking.jsonl --name c14_thinking
#
# Category key:
#   arithmetic         — exact probe format facts (matches c12_probe_multilingual.md)
#   arithmetic_de      — German arithmetic (same facts, DE surface)
#   arithmetic_jp      — Japanese arithmetic (same facts, JP surface)
#   arithmetic_zh      — Chinese arithmetic (same facts, ZH surface)
#   arithmetic_para    — paraphrase-form questions (Phase B p01-p05 surface)
#   arithmetic_grounded — object-embedded arithmetic (matches c10/c11)
#   identity           — number identity and equality (matches c01/c02)
#   comparison         — more/less/equal comparison (matches c03/c09)
#   successor          — counting and successor (matches c04)
#   zero               — zero as identity element (matches c05)
#   sequence           — number sequences and patterns (matches c13)
#   rule_application   — rule-apply (matches c14 ALeRT-style)
#   contrastive        — right/wrong discrimination (matches c15)
#   grounded_causal    — causal/sequential reasoning (grounded_stories transfer)

